grid <- seq(0.1, 8, length.out = 100)
tibble(M = grid, MSE = map_dbl(M, ~ . + 1/.)) %>% ggplot() + 
  geom_line(aes(x = M, y = MSE)) + theme(axis.text = element_blank(),
                                         axis.ticks = element_blank())
